{"tid":756610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：孤立的治安事件","createTime":"2018-07-26T07:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T08:06:08.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"246da735be8c5cceac6be45a354177248ffdf6dc","tid":756610,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:38:33.000Z","msg":"[美駐華大使館26日午間發生爆燃，外交部：孤立的治安事件]<br />\n<br />\n據多名網友爆料，7月26日13時許，在位於北京朝陽區天澤路的美國駐華大使館附近疑似發生爆炸。26日下午，有外媒記者在外交部例行發佈會上就此事向發言人提問。 發言人耿爽回應說，你可能已經注意到了，北京警方已在網上發佈消息介紹了目前的一些情況，「我想說的是，這起發生在朝陽區天澤路和安家樓路的事件是一起孤立的治安事件，中國警方已經及時地、妥善地進行了處理。」<br />\n<br />\nSource： Sina 環球網"},{"pid":"f8f9a33e9c9e36282337c26a8cf8ab3d57f0ce3c","tid":756610,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"一次就一次<br />\n起乜尻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a8a5bd6df5466c865f33f67f0b7cd885b75f5c","tid":756610,"uid":39256,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:41:04.000Z","msg":"點解我唔明佢講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcf9ba35e0af50cc5086a0cee52bf0df39a30c8","tid":756610,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"一起孤立美國駐華大使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8a8ac0df026f07b613ecce5314bc72eb2c45f2","tid":756610,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"咩叫孤立治安事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e035116335b7f68e89b5852409317a55719691","tid":756610,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"中文？"},{"pid":"c4f23bfb26dd55db679550f1036a06adbc8a17d4","tid":756610,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e8a8ac0df026f07b613ecce5314bc72eb2c45f2","tid":756610,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s